# Vendored py2jac llvmlite translation (#6925): ctypes-heavy, intentionally not
# type-clean. jac format excludes it via the find in ci.yml; this skips it
# for `jac check`. fnmatch path-pattern -> matches every file under the package.
passes/native/llvm/*
# Native wasm/LLVM emission + na_ir_gen_pass.impl ctypes-heavy submodules: bind
# raw llvmlite/llvm-c handles (is_declaration, linkage, verify, emit_object,
# create_target_machine) whose attrs the checker sees as Unknown, same class as
# na_ir_gen_pass.jac / na_compile_pass.jac above. Skipped for `jac check`.
# cycle_collector/struct/debug/trace_fn.impl.jac (#7149) are na_ir_gen_pass.impl
# LLVM-IR builder submodules in this same category (ir.GlobalVariable/ir.Constant/
# .linkage etc.), not a new kind of exclusion.
